Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.32,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.48,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:28.92,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,空彥 幫那小子實現他的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:33.67,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師父 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.66,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歐爾麥特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.74,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:44.35,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:51.84,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你們帶給我這場絕妙喜劇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.41,MHA_pic,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs90\bord0\blur5\fad(500,0)\t(0,700,\blur0)\t(\fs95)\pos(245,136)}八木俊典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.41,MHA_pic,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs90\bord0\blur5\fad(500,0)\t(0,700,\blur0)\t(\fs95)\pos(210.666,221.334)}十八歲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:59.41,MHA_pic,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs90\bord0\blur5\fad(500,0)\t(0,700,\blur0)\t(\fs95)\pos(400,306)}與其師志村菜奈訣別
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:07.17,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管哪座城市都埋有他的暗線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:11.52,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去 你也會被他殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:14.92,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不試試怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:19.41,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是要成為「和平的象徵」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:25.71,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人可是活了一百多年的怪物 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:32.29,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師父不惜付出一切 只為了將「One For All」發揚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.87,0:01:35.14,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她是位真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:39.32,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我視她為母親一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.08,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,俊典 你畢業後就到海的另一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.17,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再在他能夠觸及的地方待下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:49.10,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.25,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不堪重負的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:56.44,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道志村讓你逃走的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:58.94,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,俊典 你能理解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.21,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,積蓄力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.48,MHA_pic,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs100\bord1\blur3\fad(800,0)\move(1165,144,1115,144)\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H4F&}於是春天 八木俊典從雄英畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:14.02,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.69,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都要如同自己安然無事一樣笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:21.63,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在這世間 笑著的人是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:28.66,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,當身負拯救一切的力量時 我必定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:32.63,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作為「和平的象徵」再次踏上這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.38,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了
